<div id="splash">

  <section id="join">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h1>Join My Apnea</h1>
        <p> Be part of a Patient Powered Network that drives Sleep Apnea research by focusing on the needs of those diagnosed with Sleep Apnea.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>It's easy</li>
          <li>It's safe</li>
          <li>You can make a difference for yourself and others</li>
        </ul>
        <%= link_to "Join Now!", page_path('pledge'), class: "btn btn-block btn-primary btn-lg", id: "join-btn-top", remote: false %>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6" id="main-video">
        <div class="aspect-box">
          <div class="aspect-content">
            <iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/4JkiWvWn2aU?html5=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <section id="goal">
        <h3>Our Goal: 50,000 Signups</h3>
        <div class="aspect-box">
          <div class="aspect-content">
            <div id="goal-chart">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <section id="perils">
        <h3>The perils of Sleep Apnea:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>EDS</li>
          <li>Hypertension</li>
          <li>Heart Attack</li>
          <li>Stroke</li>
          <li>Diabetes</li>
          <li>What & why we need to understand etc</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

  </div>
  <section id="safe-easy">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class='thumbnail'><%= image_tag "pages/safe-easy.jpg" %></div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-7 col-md-offset-1">
        <h3></h3>
        <p><strong class="text-info">It's Safe!</strong><br />Your privacy and health information are protected.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-info">It's Easy!</strong><br />Simple controls, cross platform, site tour...</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="make-difference">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h3>Make a difference!</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Better treatments and patient outcomes</li>
          <li>Manage your symptoms and increase quality of life</li>
          <li>Share and find advice with other patients around the world</li>
          <li>Encourage patient involvement in scientific collaboration and research</li>
          <li>Increase awareness</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-1">
        <div class="thumbnail"><%= image_tag "pages/make-difference.jpg" %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section id="personal-stories">
    <div id="reason-carousel" class="carousel slide">
      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#reason-carousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#reason-carousel" data-slide-to="1" class=""></li>
        <li data-target="#reason-carousel" data-slide-to="2" class=""></li>
      </ol>

      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="item active">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="thumbnail"><%= image_tag "people/1.jpg" %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-1">
              <div class="vertical-center">
                <div class="cell">
                  <blockquote>
                    <p>My husband has sleep apnea. And my daughter was diagnosed at the age of 3. I want other parents to realized that kids can have this condition too.</p>
                    <footer><cite>Justine</cite></footer>
                  </blockquote>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="thumbnail"><%= image_tag "people/2.jpg" %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-1">
              <div class="vertical-center">
                <div class="cell">
                  <blockquote>
                    <p>My wife told me I stopped breathing while I slept. A lot. Thankfully she read an article on sleep apnea and made me go to the Doctor. I donâ€™t want other people to suffer needlessly from this condition.</p>
                    <footer><cite>Steve</cite></footer>
                  </blockquote>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="thumbnail"><%= image_tag "people/3.jpg" %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-1">
              <div class="vertical-center">
                <div class="cell">
                  <blockquote>
                    <p>
                      I have always been a snorer - I had no idea it was more than just a nuisance to my partner. I have lowered my blood pressure and my chances of heart disease by wearing a CPAP. I want to be a part of the study to find out what else is effected by this condition.
                    </p>
                    <footer><cite>Richard</cite></footer>
                  </blockquote>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="left carousel-control" href="#reason-carousel" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="icon-prev"></span>
      </a>
      <a class="right carousel-control" href="#reason-carousel" data-slide="next">
        <span class="icon-next"></span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<%= render partial: 'layouts/join_bottom' %>
